Requests - Spring 2023

GUIDELINES

First off: Thank you for considering me for commission.
My requests this round are simple, with a pay-what-you-want scale starting at $5.
  • I hold the right to refuse any commission if I feel my abilities are not adequate for your request.
  • All commissions are done on a first come, first serve basis
  • Commission completion will vary by piece. It usually takes me a day or two unless someone is in front of you.
  • Please elaborate exactly what it is you want done. Pictures and references, oc profiles and descriptions help a whole bunch! The more reference I have, the better I can make your idea come to life.

This price point holds no bars. You can have just a simple sketch to a full blown painted potrait for only $5. The only exception to this rule is a reference sheet, which is minimum 20$ instead because it is technically a 3-in-1 sketch.
If you do not check the add-on box during your request, and I confirm this is your choice, I will draw your character T-posing in a maid outfit of my choosing instead of a reference sheet.

All communication will be done through Ko-fi.

Will Do

✅ OC DESIGNS*
✅ FANART
✅ VTUBERS

Workflow

Research
& Reference

You tell me what you need, I will give you an Idea of whether or not I can provide the skillset for you. I look up references that I may need for the peice.

Drafting
& Review

I draft up multiple poses and ideas by thumbnailing different ideas for the work until you are satisfied.

Coloring
& Rendering

Once a draft is selected, I begin adding color and rendering the piece, adding color, lighting, and shadows.

Confirmation
& Completion

I show you the finished work for a final review, ensure that the picce is to your liking, and confirm the work is complete,
